| # | Series | Construction | Purpose |
|---|--------|--------------|---------|
| 19 | **Regional Spread Correlation** | Rolling 60-day corr($\Delta S_{\text{US}}, \Delta S_{\text{EU}}$) | Cross-border contagion |
| 20 | **Equity-Bond Correlation** | Rolling 60-day corr($R_{\text{SPX}}, R_{\text{10Y}}$) | Risk-on/off regime |
| 21 | **Correlation Dispersion** | $\sigma(\rho_{ij,t})$ across asset pairs | Systemic risk |

### 5.4 VAR Specification

**Vector:**
$$\mathbf{y}_t = [\mathbf{s}_t, \mathbf{f}_t, \mathbf{c}_t]^\top \in \mathbb{R}^{21}$$

**Reduced Form:**
$$\mathbf{y}_t = \sum_{p=1}^{5} \mathbf{A}_p \mathbf{y}_{t-p} + \mathbf{u}_t$$

**Structural Identification (Cholesky Ordering):**
1. Funding liquidity (exogenous)
2. Market liquidity
3. Volatility
4. Credit
5. Spreads
6. Contagion

