## 6. SPY:TLT Ratio Index

**Total Inputs:** 2 ETF price series  
**Frequency:** Intraday (1-min bars) or daily (EOD)  
**Transformation:** Log ratio, then optional z-score normalization

### 6.1 Primary Inputs (2)

| # | Series | Ticker | Asset Class | Frequency | Source |
|---|--------|--------|-------------|-----------|--------|
| 1 | **SPDR S&P 500 ETF** | SPY | US Large-Cap Equity | 1-min OHLCV | Bloomberg/Polygon |
| 2 | **iShares 20+ Year Treasury ETF** | TLT | US Long-Duration Bonds | 1-min OHLCV | Bloomberg/Polygon |

### 6.2 Derived Index

**Formula:**
$$\text{RORO}_t^{\text{Ratio}} = \log\left(\frac{P_t^{\text{SPY}}}{P_t^{\text{TLT}}}\right)$$

**Normalization (optional):**
$$\text{RORO}_t^{\text{Ratio,z}} = \frac{\text{RORO}_t^{\text{Ratio}} - \mu_W}{\sigma_W}$$

where $\mu_W, \sigma_W$ computed over rolling window $W=252$ days.

### 6.3 Momentum Overlay

**Moving Average Crossover:**
$$\text{Signal}_t = \mathbb{1}\{\text{MA}_5(\text{RORO}_t) > \text{MA}_{20}(\text{RORO}_t)\}$$

**RSI Indicator:**
$$\text{RSI}_t = 100 - \frac{100}{1 + RS_t}, \quad RS_t = \frac{\text{Avg(Up)}_{\text{14}}}{\text{Avg(Down)}_{\text{14}}}$$

### 6.4 Missing: Options-Based Enhancements

**PROPOSED ADDITIONS:**

| # | Variable | Construction | Rationale |
|---|----------|--------------|-----------|
| 3 | **SPY-TLT Implied Correlation** | Implied corr from spread option | Direct regime measure |
| 4 | **SPY Put Skew** | 25Δ put IV - 25Δ call IV | Equity tail risk |
| 5 | **TLT Realized-Implied Vol Spread** | RV - IV | Bond market stress |

