## 9. Williams %R Index

**Total Inputs:** 10 ETF price series (same as MAC)  
**Frequency:** Daily or intraday  
**Transformation:** Composite of risk-safe, then Williams %R oscillator

### 9.1 Inputs (10 ETFs - identical to Section 8)

Same risk and safe baskets as MAC Index.

### 9.2 Composite Construction

**Step 1: Risk Basket Average**
$$C_t^{\text{risk}} = \frac{1}{5} \sum_{a \in \text{Risk}} P_{a,t}$$

**Step 2: Safe Basket Average**
$$C_t^{\text{safe}} = \frac{1}{5} \sum_{a \in \text{Safe}} P_{a,t}$$

**Step 3: Differential**
$$\text{Composite}_t = C_t^{\text{risk}} - C_t^{\text{safe}}$$

### 9.3 Williams %R Calculation

**Formula:**
$$\text{RORO}_t^{\text{WR}} = -100 \times \frac{\max_{s \in [t-L, t]}(\text{Composite}_s) - \text{Composite}_t}{\max_{s \in [t-L, t]}(\text{Composite}_s) - \min_{s \in [t-L, t]}(\text{Composite}_s)}$$

where $L = 14$ is lookback period.

**Range:** $[-100, 0]$
- $> -50$: Risk-on
- $< -50$: Risk-off

### 9.4 Missing: Volume-Weighted Version

**PROPOSED ADDITION:**

| Variable | Construction | Rationale |
|----------|--------------|-----------|
| **Volume-Weighted Composite** | $\sum_a w_{a,t} P_{a,t}$ where $w_{a,t} \propto \text{Volume}_{a,t}$ | More liquid assets get higher weight |

